title.narrative: Premises and Security

description.narrative: Building on previous years, GCO continues to prioritize the advancement of children, adolescents; and women’s active participation in decision making, positive behaviour change and demand creation. Progress continued in strengthening local government decentralized structures, through the UNICEF-UNDP led partnership; to create engaging opportunities that foster civic empowerment and engagement for collective action and communication for development to support positive change. Children, adolescents and women nationwide participated in the development of the Situation Analysis of Children and Adolescents through regional consultations with members of the Children National Assembly, senior secondary school councilors, VSGs, VDCs, CCPCs, mothers clubs and womens’ groups. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:06/01/2022
